data.text:
Joplin, Missouri, USA

Latitude and longitude coordinates are: 37.084229, -94.513283.

Joplin is a city in southwestern Missouri, with the number of residents close to 175,000 people. "Proud of Our Past...Shaping Our Future" is the motto of the city. It was named after one of the earliest settlers from Europe. Joplin is a business and industrial city, with a few small commercial and manufacturing companies operating at the market.
